<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-11-18T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-11-18T15:00:00-05:00" n="258" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d258">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/2535: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland (<persName corresp="#p_WHR1" type="from">Wilson</persName>) to the
                                        <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-11-18T21:00:00+01:00">November 18, 1932—9 p.m.</date>
                                    <lb/> [Received November 18—3:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>44. Your 34, November 17, 7 p.m., caused great satisfaction to
                                    <persName corresp="#p_DSE1">Drummond</persName>. He has noted
                                the alteration suggested in relation to points 2 and 3 and quite
                                understands its advantage. He has requested me to put <persName corresp="#p_DVE1">De Valera</persName> in touch with the
                                situation on his arrival tomorrow which I shall do.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_WHR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>